    <item>
      <title>急于通过关税豁免突然停止黄金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/rush-to-get-gold-to-the-us-halts-abruptly-with-tariff-exemption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项大规模的套利交易吸引了数万美元的黄金和白银，突然停止了，周三宣布，贵金属将免于唐纳德·特朗普的大量关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/rush-to-get-gold-to-the-us-halts-abruptly-with-tariff-exemption</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 09:27:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税公告会影响石油市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-03/trump-tariffs-announcement-impacts-oil-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统在他对主要贸易伙伴的关税计划中保留了能源，但石油市场对税收可能影响贸易战的粗略需求产生了负面反应。斯图尔特·利文斯通·沃拉斯（Stuart Livingstone-Wallace）在中东，北非和俄罗斯的执行编辑告诉地平线中东和非洲主持人乔曼娜·贝尔科奇（Joumanna Bercetche），关税对中东经济的影响将很慢。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-03/trump-tariffs-announcement-impacts-oil-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 09:26:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SNB的Tschudin说，特朗普的瑞士关税高于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-s-swiss-tariffs-higher-than-expected-snb-s-tschudin-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士国家银行董事会成员彼得拉·汤丁（Petra Tschudin）表示，美国决定以31％的关税打击瑞士的税率比预期的要高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-s-swiss-tariffs-higher-than-expected-snb-s-tschudin-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 09:25:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挪威房价以自去年七月以来的最慢速度上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/norway-home-prices-rise-at-slowest-pace-since-last-july</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威调整后的房价在八个月内提高了最慢的速度，因为消费者变得更加谨慎，而货币宽松后不断推迟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/norway-home-prices-rise-at-slowest-pace-since-last-july</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 09:22:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场尚未以20％的欧洲关税价格定价：曼西</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-03/market-has-not-priced-in-20-tariffs-for-europe-manthey-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗欧洲股票战略主管首席Beata Manthey讨论了美国总统唐纳德·特朗普可能对市场和包括英国在内的更广泛的欧洲经济体产生的影响。她说，市场“欧洲的价格尚未以20％的价格定价”，并补充说，美国对欧洲的征收和潜在的个人部门关税可能“约为3％的EPS（每股收益）影响”。曼西在彭博电视台上说：“最大的担忧当然是对经济的二阶影响。” （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-03/market-has-not-priced-in-20-tariffs-for-europe-manthey-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 09:04:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税威胁需求和经济，商品袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/commodities-hit-as-trump-s-tariffs-threaten-demand-and-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从石油到工业金属到谷物的商品，唐纳德·特朗普总统对猛击的关税造成了一场贸易战，这有可能损害全球经济和对原材料的需求。在获得新的纪录后，黄金稳定了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/commodities-hit-as-trump-s-tariffs-threaten-demand-and-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 08:57:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元交易者准备货币幻灯片后的更多损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/dollar-slides-on-concern-trump-s-tariffs-will-batter-us-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统的全面贸易关税使美国货币削弱了两年半以来，贸易商正在以更多的美元弱点来削弱美元的弱点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/dollar-slides-on-concern-trump-s-tariffs-will-batter-us-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 04:01:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普的关税增加了全球增长的风险时，害怕抓住市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/fear-grips-markets-as-trump-tariffs-raise-risks-to-global-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着通过全球市场级联的损失，交易者正在迅速意识到他们对唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税的最糟糕情况都是真实的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/fear-grips-markets-as-trump-tariffs-raise-risks-to-global-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 22:43:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税宽边向全球经济带来冲击波</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-says-he-s-signing-executive-order-on-reciprocal-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统在一个世纪内征收美国最陡峭的美国关税，他加强了重塑全球经济的竞选活动，引发了报复的威胁，并在全球市场上抛弃了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-says-he-s-signing-executive-order-on-reciprocal-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 20:16:31 GMT</pubDate>
